It's the FIVE YEAR ANNIVERSARY of the creation of Comic Book Clique! To celebrate in style we decided to tell our OWN origin story for what would eventually become the latest and greatest thing to come to comic books and comic book media. How did CBC start? Did you know CBC was almost called something entirely different? What is in store for the next five years for the company. All that and more in this heartfelt, and honest look at one of the most rewarding journeys of all time.   Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media. Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! Please [SUPPORT US ON PATREON](http://Patreon.com/CBCClubhouse)!

